[3] UK (Wales)
Date: Mon 14 Oct 2013
Source: ITV News[edited]
http://www.itv.com/news/wales/update/2013-10-14/public-health-wales-notified-of-four-new-measles-cases/


There are 2 confirmed cases at a school in Neath Port Talbot. It's believed there are a further 4 cases of measles in South West Wales. Public Health Wales say there are now 7 cases associated with Cwmtawe School in Neath Port Talbot, 2 of which have been confirmed in laboratory tests.

Last week [week of 7 Oct 2013], 2 cases were identified in children in another school in Powys, and these are connected to one of the confirmed cases at Cwmtawe School.

